{"type":"message","id":"f3a63581","parentId":"b38b364a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:19:05.592Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个会话是我自己（cron任务），并不是活跃的用户对话。我需要再次检查是否有真正的用户对话。让我检查一下是否有其他会话，或者检查当前会话的时间戳。\n\n从返回结果来看，只有一个会话，就是这个cron任务本身（agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978）。这说明没有活跃的用户对话。\n\n但我需要更仔细地判断。activeMinutes设为5，意味着查询最近5分钟内有更新的会话。这个cron任务本身就是当前的会话，所以它显示为\"活跃\"。\n\n实际上，我应该检查的是有没有真实用户发起的会话，而不是cron任务本身。让我用更长的activeMinutes或者检查sessions列表中是否有用户的会话。\n\n实际上，从sessions_list的返回来看，只有一个session，就是当前的cron任务。没有其他用户会话。这说明没有活跃对话。\n\n但是我需要更仔细地理解\"活跃对话\"的定义。让我看看sessions列表中是否有其他会话...\n\n从返回结果来看，`\"sessions\": [...]`只有一个元素就是这个cron任务本身。这意味着在最近5分钟内没有真实的用户对话。\n\n我应该执行自主学习任务。\n\n现在我需要搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成和IT运维服务相关的最新行业动态。","thinkingSignature":"aa910d210b9a4ce01910c2feb7e2b5ee33d0a1362f0cff30aff5446db1098ac4"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有cron任务会话，没有真实用户对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f265fu8dj6bg_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":824,"output":308,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45113,"cost":{"input":0.0002472,"output":0.0003696,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00193623}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774682335240}}
{"type":"message","id":"e40bf6b6","parentId":"f3a63581","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:19:05.599Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f265fu8dj6bg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774682345595}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0ee13b5","parentId":"e40bf6b6","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:19:11.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要使用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索相关信息。让我搜索几个相关关键词：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业趋势\n3. 网络系统集成最新技术\n4. IT运维服务行业动态\n\n让我并行搜索这些关键词。","thinkingSignature":"445140b2f0fd292e33338b91a82f39edbac1a91e899fd46f87f42f197c5934a7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eizaph4wfqxd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新动态 政策\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eizaph4wfqxd_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 行业趋势 2026\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eizaph4wfqxd_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 行业动态 2026\" --output json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1647,"output":192,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45820,"cost":{"input":0.0004941,"output":0.0002304,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00204393}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774682345598}}
